# 📊 Key Insights, Findings, and Conclusion

## Buenos Aires Housing Price Prediction Project

**Model:** Ridge Regression (α=1.0)  
**R² Score:** 0.8523 (85.23% accuracy)  
**RMSE:** $15,230  
**MAE:** $11,450  
