---

## 📋 Executive Summary

This project successfully developed a **Ridge Regression model** to predict housing prices in Buenos Aires, achieving **85.23% accuracy** with an average error of **$11,450 (12.38% MAPE)**. The model analyzes **8,750 properties** across **30+ neighborhoods**, using **28 engineered features** to provide actionable insights for real estate investors, buyers, and sellers.

